'''布魯斯特·路頓·卡利'''（'''Brewster Lurton Kahle''' {{IPAc-en|ˈ|k|eɪ|l}} {{respell|KAYL|<nowiki>'</nowiki>}}；<ref>Schwartz, John, [http://www.nytimes.com/2001/10/29/technology/ebusiness/29NECO.html "Page by Page History of the Web"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2001/10/29/technology/ebusiness/29NECO.html |date=20160304073325 }}, ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'', October 29, 2001</ref> {{bd|1960年}}）<ref name="juggle">[http://www.juggle.com/alexa-internet Alexa Internet profile] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717045807/http://www.juggle.com/alexa-internet |date=2011-07-17 }}, via juggle.com. Last accessed November 24, 2010</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nndb.com/people/831/000124459/ |title=Brewster Kahle |publisher=NNDB |date= |accessdate=January 19, 2012 |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225202226/https://www.nndb.com/people/831/000124459/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 是一位美國數字圖書館員、電腦工程師和資訊科技企業家，是[[Alexa_Internet|Alexa Internet]]和[[互联网档案馆|互联网档案馆]]的創始人。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.sfgate.com/default/article/Brewster-Kahle-s-Internet-Archive-3946898.php |title=Brewster Kahle's Internet Archive |work=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]] |date=October 13, 2012 |accessdate=October 13, 2012 |author=Benny Evangelista |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225121209/https://www.sfgate.com/default/article/Brewster-Kahle-s-Internet-Archive-3946898.php |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2012年入選[[網際網路名人堂|網際網路名人堂]]，<ref>[http://www.internethalloffame.org/inductees/year/2012 2012 Inductees] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DdpUIbPU?url=http://www.internethalloffame.org/inductees/year/2012 |date=20130113133323 |dateformat=iso }}, [[Internet_Hall_of_Fame|Internet Hall of Fame]] website. Last accessed April 24, 2012</ref> 此外也是[[美國文理科學院|美國文理科學院]]院士、[[美國國家工程院|美國國家工程院]]成員、[[電子前線基金會|電子前線基金會]]、[[公共知識|公共知識]]、[[網絡記憶基金會|網絡記憶基金會]]等組織的董事會成員。

==生平==
[[File:Internet-archive-brewster-kahle-2013-0329.webm|thumb]]
卡利出生於[[紐約州|紐約州]][[紐約市|紐約市]]的郊區[[斯卡斯代爾|斯卡斯代爾]]，在[[斯卡斯代爾高中|斯卡斯代爾高中]]讀書。後來考入[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]]，1982年以[[計算機科學|計算機科學]]和[[計算機工程|計算機工程]][[理學學士|理學學士]]學位畢業。<ref name=edu/><ref>[http://mitadmissions.org/blogs/entry/internet_nostalgia Internet Nostalgia | MIT Admissions] {{Wayback|url=http://mitadmissions.org/blogs/entry/internet_nostalgia |date=20191121084226 }} ''MIT Admissions''. Retrieved July 11, 2011.</ref> 其學習重心為[[人工智能|人工智能]]，曾接受[[馬文·閔斯基|馬文·閔斯基]]和[[丹尼尔·希利斯|丹尼尔·希利斯]]的教導。<ref name=edu>[http://brewster.kahle.org/about/ About] {{Wayback|url=http://brewster.kahle.org/about/ |date=20110812051411 }} ''Brewster Kahle's Blog''. Retrieved July 11, 2011.</ref>

畢業後於1983年到1989年間在[[思考機器公司|思考機器公司]]的[[連接機|連接機]]產品擔任首席工程師，在這裡卡利開發了[[廣域信息伺服器|廣域信息伺服器]]系統。1996年與Bruce Gilliat創辦WAIS, Inc.（1995年以1500萬美元賣給[[AOL|AOL]]），1996年創辦了[[Alexa_Internet|Alexa Internet]]<ref name=LAtimes>{{cite news|last=Kellogg|first=Carolyn|title=Archiving every book ever published|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/jacketcopy/2011/08/archiving-every-book-ever-published.html|accessdate=18 August 2011|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=August 5, 2011{{!}} 10:16 am|archive-date=2019-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524103349/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/jacketcopy/2011/08/archiving-every-book-ever-published.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>（1999年將價值2.5億美元的股份賣給了[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]]）。同時亦創立了[[互联网档案馆|互联网档案馆]]。<ref name=NYtimes>{{cite news|last=TONG|first=JUDY|title=RESPONSIBLE PARTY – BREWSTER KAHLE; A Library Of the Web, On the Web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2002/09/08/business/responsible-party-brewster-kahle-a-library-of-the-web-on-the-web.html|accessdate=18 August 2011|newspaper=New York Times|date=September 8, 2002|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308200607/https://www.nytimes.com/2002/09/08/business/responsible-party-brewster-kahle-a-library-of-the-web-on-the-web.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

凱利和他的妻子瑪麗·奧斯丁（Mary Austin）運營著卡利/奧斯丁基金會。該基金會支持著[[自由軟件基金會|自由軟件基金會]]的[[GNU計劃|GNU計劃]]等。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gnu.org/thankgnus/2011supporters.html |title=Thank GNUs 2011 |publisher=Free Software Foundation |date= |accessdate=January 19, 2012 |archive-date=2020-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228023329/http://www.gnu.org/thankgnus/2011supporters.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2011年共提供約450萬美元資金。<ref>[[Form_990|Form 990]] data from http://fdo.foundationcenter.org/grantmaker-profile?key=KAHL009 {{Wayback|url=http://fdo.foundationcenter.org/grantmaker-profile?key=KAHL009 |date=20150402162643 }}</ref>

